彈，而身為首席創意官嘅王祖藍，在直播後接受訪問時，表示「希望以開放態度，可以嬉笑怒罵一點，望無綫有新嘅改革。」<br />\n<br />\n《開心大綜藝》既然肩負重任，面對ViuTV周日（18日）將舉行首個音樂頒獎禮《Chill Club推介榜 年度推介20/21》，有傳無綫準備將《開心大綜藝》由原先一小時加碼至兩小時，實行加重料用作對撼。雖然曾志偉曾直言「友台僅得約4點收視，加上節目題材亦較為偏門，只可以與J2作比較而非翡翠台對手」，但有傳當得知ViuTV有意邀陳奕迅出席18號頒獎禮後，曾打算搶頭啖湯，請Eason現身首集《開心大綜藝》，唯最後Eason拒絕了兩邊的邀請。明確地顯示新電視台大戰將愈來愈精彩。<br />\n<br />\n不過對於有關加時嘅傳聞，身為《開心大綜藝》主持人之一嘅林盛斌接受《香港01》訪問時，就表示：「完全冇聽過，不過就算加，其實應該同上一集一樣，主持人都係一日綵排，一日on show，其他有表演環節嘅同事就可能要排多啲時間。」TVB肯變，對觀眾一定有好處。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210413/458726726403362816497682.jpeg/U8r_9Hrkf_KZdz43m5pWHRuPrkLfRhvywXzRBcF80QU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210413%2F458726726403362816497682.jpeg%2FU8r_9Hrkf_KZdz43m5pWHRuPrkLfRhvywXzRBcF80QU&h=d53e7aae&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"TVB收皮啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11994c5af4203acbbfa26e71757827e981a529f0","tid":2488152,"uid":312470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"哪來的自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebb6dc7498c0f7419be1ba1084577e83203c7a8","tid":2488152,"uid":125888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"睇左3分鐘 youtube個記者會<br />\n真心笑唔出 可能又扮女人<br />\n仲衰撚過以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9c23819d782adc4fd949f9bca570705b3e67a1","tid":2488152,"uid":274921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/ass